org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd

Class CDEXTFIELD

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.AbstractStruct
      • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDRecord
        • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDEXTFIELD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public class CDEXTFIELD
extends CDRecord
    New field attributes have been added in Release 4.0 of Notes. To preserve compatibility with existing applications, the new attributes have been placed in this extension to the CDFIELD record. This record is optional, and may not be present in the $Body item of the form note. (editods.h)
    Since:
    Lotus Notes 4.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
